Funcional:
  1. Donation system
    1.1. Purpose specific donations with feedback
    1.2. General purpose donations
    1.3. Campaign donations with feedback on completion progress
  2. Prayer request system
  3. Optionaly get user e-mail to later contact

Non-Functional:
